==English==

===Noun===
'''facebook'''  (''plural:'' '''facebooks''')

# A [[reference]] [[book]] made up of individuals' [[photographs]] and names. 
# A [[college]] [[publication]] distributed at the start of the academic year by [[university]] [[administration]]s with the intention of helping [[students]] get to know each other better.
#:''The shipment of facebooks be distributed to the freshman during orientation and move-in-week.''

